title: The Daily Warrior Protocol: Meditation 3-Pack - Gabi Robledo
author: Gabi Robledo
description: This 3-pack meditation series is designed to perfectly attune the mind for complete balance and mastery through a morning, a midday, and an evening guided meditation. Through activation of Alpha and Theta brainwaves, you'll quickly instill a healthy flow of brainwaves which shapes your brains to be happier, helps cultivate a creative and purposeful existence, and allows you to tap into a high performance state more easily.
cleaned_text: Ready to master your mind, eliminate your stress & anxiety, and optimize your brain's neuropathways for success? This meditation series is for you! The Daily Warrior Protocol: Meditation 3-Pack $27.00 - This 3-pack meditation series is designed to perfectly attune the mind for complete balance and mastery through a morning, a midday, and an evening guided meditation. Through activation of Alpha and Theta brainwaves, you'll quickly instill a healthy flow of brainwaves which shapes your brains to be happier, helps cultivate a creative and purposeful existence, and allows you to tap into a high performance state more easily.
